 of Education (March 21, 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pde.state.pa.us/portal/server.pt/community/departmental_offices/7235\">\"Pennsylvania Department of Education Departmental Offices\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Pennsylvania+Department+of+Education+Departmental+Offices&amp;rft.date=2014-03-21&amp;rft.au=Pennsylvania+Department+of+Education&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pde.state.pa.us%2Fportal%2Fserver.pt%2Fcommunity%2Fdepartmental_offices%2F7235&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APennsylvania+Department+of+Education\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">News and Media (2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pde.state.pa.us/portal/server.pt/community/news_and_media/7234\">\"PDE News and Media\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=PDE+News+and+Media&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.au=News+and+Media&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pde.state.pa.us%2Fportal%2Fserver.pt%2Fcommunity%2Fnews_and_media%2F7234&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APennsylvania+Department+of+Education\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">PDE, Enrollment by County 2013-14, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.portal.state.pa.us/portal/server.pt